funny.bio: We’ve made switching browsers easy, fast and risk-free, so when you try the new Firefox you can concentrate on how smooth it runs. And with Firefox, you’re getting the latest internet technology, stability and security, all in context with your stuff—bookmarks, autofills, passwords, preferences, accounts.
funny.strains: You can use Firefox and still have Chrome. Chrome won’t change on your machine one bit.
funny.sponsorTagline: Switching to Firefox is easy and risk-free!
